            h5 Scheduling accounts

            p Accounts that get triaged into the planner for scheduling will appear in a fixed "scheduling" container, with markers on the map so users can compare and see what makes sense to add to the day's schedule.

            p A simple drag and drop mechanism will add it to the schedule of the date the user is viewing. To make the mechanism more learnable, I included a small line of instructions under each section to prompt user interaction.

