            h5 Giving feedback on a customer interaction

            p One of the pain points we heard was around interacting with the CMS, and I wanted to brainstorm ways it could be improved. One of the ideas we came up with was a voice-to-text note taker, so the sales reps' immediate reactions to customers could be captured more easily.

