          .body-section-content

            p Ultimately the goal of this app is to improve sales performance. Total revenue increases are definitely going to be the metric that interest businesses purchasing this tool for their sales reps.

            p More granularly, tracking click throughs and comparing them to changes in customer churn and acquisition can help improve the UX of the app through its future product iterations, as well as the AI recommendation algorithm.

